# AI Homepage Prompt Library (Modular Buttons)

Use each section as an independent prompt users can edit before generating content.

---

## 🔹 HERO SECTION

**Prompt:**

Write a high-converting, SEO-optimized hero section for **[Business Name]**, a **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Create a headline (6–10 words) using **[primary keyword]**
- Write a subheadline (1 sentence) including **[secondary keywords]** and **[unique value proposition]**
- Add a strong CTA button (2–4 words), e.g., **[Book Now / Get Started / Shop Now]**

**Goal:** Grab attention instantly and communicate value clearly.

---

## 🔹 TITLE (PAGE / SEO TITLE)

**Prompt:**

Write an SEO-optimized title tag for **[Business Name]**, a **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Include **[primary keyword]**
- Optionally include **[secondary keyword]**
- Keep it under 60 characters
- Make it compelling for search results (click-worthy)

---

## 🔹 WELCOME SECTION

**Prompt:**

Write an engaging, SEO-optimized welcome section (max 2 sentences) for **[Business Name]**, a **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Include **[primary keyword] + [location]**
- Mention **[core services/products]** and **[target audience]**
- Highlight **[unique value proposition]**
- Do NOT start with "Welcome to"
- Keep it short, inviting, and benefit-driven

---

## 🔹 ABOUT US

**Prompt:**

Write an SEO-friendly "About Us" section (3–5 sentences) for **[Business Name]**, a **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Include **[primary keyword]** naturally
- Describe **[brand story / mission / experience]**
- Highlight **[what makes the business unique]**
- Mention **[target audience or community served]**
- Keep tone aligned with **[brand voice: luxury / playful / corporate / family-friendly]**

---

## 🔹 VALUE PROPOSITION BULLETS

**Prompt:**

Write 3–5 concise, SEO-friendly value proposition bullets for **[Business Name]**.

- Focus on **[quality / experience / pricing / speed / trust]**
- Each bullet must be under 10 words
- Use action-oriented, customer-focused language
- Optionally include **[keywords]** naturally

---

## 🔹 CTA SECTION

**Prompt:**

Write a persuasive, SEO-optimized call-to-action section for **[Business Name]**, a **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Write 1–2 compelling sentences
- Include **[primary keyword] + [location]**
- Reinforce **[benefits or urgency]**
- End with a strong CTA button label (2–4 words)

---

## 🔹 CONTACT US

**Prompt:**

Write a friendly, SEO-aware "Contact Us" section (2–3 sentences) for **[Business Name]**, a **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Encourage users to reach out for **[services/products]**
- Include **[location]** and **[primary keyword]**
- Mention **[phone/email/visit/storefront if applicable]**
- Keep tone approachable and action-driven

---

## 🔹 OPTIONAL SEO BOOST

**Prompt:**

Enhance the content with 3–5 natural keyword variations for **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

- Avoid keyword stuffing
- Maintain readability and flow
- Align with **[brand voice]**

